  "name": "Škály částic",
  "order": 2,
  "notebookEntry": {
    "content": "<h2>Škály částic</h2>\n<p>Svět kolem nás se skládá z částic různých velikostí — od subatomárních po makroskopické.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 500 120' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <line x1='30' y1='60' x2='470' y2='60' stroke='#d1d5db' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <circle cx='50' cy='60' r='6' fill='#ef4444'/><text x='50' y='40' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444' font-size='11' font-weight='bold'>jádro</text><text x='50' y='85' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='10'>10⁻¹⁵ m</text><circle cx='140' cy='60' r='6' fill='#f59e0b'/><text x='140' y='40' text-anchor='middle' fill='#f59e0b' font-size='11' font-weight='bold'>atom</text><text x='140' y='85' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='10'>10⁻¹⁰ m</text><circle cx='230' cy='60' r='6' fill='#22c55e'/><text x='230' y='40' text-anchor='middle' fill='#22c55e' font-size='11' font-weight='bold'>molekula</text><text x='230' y='85' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='10'>10⁻⁹ m</text><circle cx='320' cy='60' r='6' fill='#3b82f6'/><text x='320' y='40' text-anchor='middle' fill='#3b82f6' font-size='11' font-weight='bold'>buňka</text><text x='320' y='85' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='10'>10⁻⁶ m</text><circle cx='410' cy='60' r='6' fill='#8b5cf6'/><text x='410' y='40' text-anchor='middle' fill='#8b5cf6' font-size='11' font-weight='bold'>zrnko</text><text x='410' y='85' text-anchor='middle' fill='#6b7280' font-size='10'>10⁻³ m</text>\n  <text x='50' y='110' fill='#6b7280' font-size='11'>← menší</text>\n  <text x='410' y='110' fill='#6b7280' font-size='11' text-anchor='end'>větší →</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Velikosti částic</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Částice</th><th>Velikost</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>Proton, neutron</td><td>≈ 10⁻¹⁵ m (1 fm)</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Atom</td><td>≈ 10⁻¹⁰ m (0,1 nm)</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Molekula vody</td><td>≈ 3 × 10⁻¹⁰ m</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Molekula DNA</td><td>≈ 2 nm šířka</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Virus</td><td>≈ 100 nm</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Červená krvinka</td><td>≈ 7 μm</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Zrnko písku</td><td>≈ 1 mm</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Předpony jednotek</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Předpona</th><th>Symbol</th><th>Násobek</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>nano</td><td>n</td><td>10⁻⁹</td></tr>\n<tr><td>mikro</td><td>μ</td><td>10⁻⁶</td></tr>\n<tr><td>mili</td><td>m</td><td>10⁻³</td></tr>\n<tr><td>kilo</td><td>k</td><td>10³</td></tr>\n<tr><td>mega</td><td>M</td><td>10⁶</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>"
  }
}
